}}'''華裔印度人囚禁'''（{{lang-en|Internment of Chinese Indians}}）是指1962年[[中印边境战争|中印戰爭]]期間印度對數千[[印度華人|華裔印度人]]在'''[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉札斯坦邦]]代奧利(Deoli)'''的囚禁和拘留。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=史海鉤沉：中印1962年邊界戰爭後印度華人落難史|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53083755|newspaper=BBC News 中文|accessdate=2021-01-20|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003142958/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53083755|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=The 1962 Internment of Chinese Indians|url=https://thediplomat.com/2020/09/the-1962-internment-of-chinese-indians/|accessdate=2021-01-20|work=thediplomat.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031232415/https://thediplomat.com/2020/09/the-1962-internment-of-chinese-indians/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The shameful story of how 3,000 Chinese-Indians were put in a detention camp is revealed in new book|url=https://scroll.in/article/948731/the-shameful-story-of-how-3000-chinese-indians-were-put-in-a-detention-camp-is-revealed-in-new-book|accessdate=2021-01-20|last=Fernandes|first=Naresh|work=Scroll.in|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118173952/https://scroll.in/article/948731/the-shameful-story-of-how-3000-chinese-indians-were-put-in-a-detention-camp-is-revealed-in-new-book|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Persecution of Chinese Indians|url=https://frontline.thehindu.com/the-nation/persecution-of-chinese-indians/article6715774.ece|accessdate=2021-01-20|last=NOORANI|first=A. G.|work=Frontline|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213160055/https://frontline.thehindu.com/the-nation/persecution-of-chinese-indians/article6715774.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=The Deoliwallahs|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=wUHHDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=the+deoliwallahs&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjspKS53KnuAhVpKqYKHQDbBisQ6AEwAHoECAAQAg#v=onepage&q=the%20deoliwallahs&f=false|publisher=Pan Macmillan|date=2020-01-23|isbn=978-1-5290-4886-5|language=en|first=Joy|last=Ma|first2=Dilip|last2=D'Souza}}</ref>

1962年中印戰爭爆發，[[印度政府|印度政府]]出於國安理由通過《國防法》（Defence of India Act 1962），授權政府於同年開始可以不經法律程序「逮捕和拘留任何（懷疑）有敵對出身的人」。<ref name=":0" /> 在此《國防法》下，所有持有華人血統、姓名、或樣貌近似華人的人都有被捕的可能。此時被捕的華裔印度人雖然有華裔血脈，卻已經在印度定居了好幾代。<ref name=":0" />有一些是十八至十九世紀從中國移居印度的華人後裔。<ref name=":1" />

據估計, 印度有多達2萬至4萬華人被逼遷徙, 數以千計的華人被抓。當中大約7500人獲准離開印度，前往西方國家如澳洲、英國、加拿大、美國,以及香港、日本等東亞地方。同時, 其他財力不足或不自願離開的華人被印度政府進行長期拘留，很多被押送到印度西北部[[拉贾斯坦邦|拉賈斯坦邦]]的代奧利拘留營（Deoli Internment Camp）。在1962年至1967年期間，有3000多名華人被關押在此[[集中营|集中营]]或印度其他地方，當中六成被關押的華裔為老人及兒童。<ref name=":0" />受害人被拘留的時間不一，有些被拘禁長達四年。<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|title=How Chinese-Indians paid the price for 1962 war|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-35593141|newspaper=BBC News|date=2016-02-18|accessdate=2021-01-20|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204010201/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-35593141|dead-url=no}}</ref>

中印戰爭後，被拘禁、驅逐或者遷移至外地的印度華人就此事向印度政府進行公開抗議。<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Chinese-Indians are terrified’: stand-off raises spectre of 1962 war|url=https://www.scmp.com/week-asia/politics/article/3097275/chinese-india-are-terrified-sos-canada-border-stand-raises|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2020-08-15|work=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230053013/https://www.scmp.com/week-asia/politics/article/3097275/chinese-india-are-terrified-sos-canada-border-stand-raises|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Silent for Decades, Chinese-Indians Interned at Deoli After 1962 War Are Ready to Speak|url=https://thewire.in/external-affairs/deoli-internment-camp-chinese-indian-prisoners|accessdate=2021-01-20|work=The Wire|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227060735/https://thewire.in/external-affairs/deoli-internment-camp-chinese-indian-prisoners|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=When India locked up 3,000 Chinese-Indians in internment camps, with Dilip D’Souza|url=https://indianexpress.com/audio/the-sandip-roy-show/when-india-locked-up-3000-chinese-indians-in-internment-camps-with-dilip-dsouza/6325846/|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2020-03-22|work=The Indian Express|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308083447/https://indianexpress.com/audio/the-sandip-roy-show/when-india-locked-up-3000-chinese-indians-in-internment-camps-with-dilip-dsouza/6325846/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1998年，印度華人被允許恢復印度[[國籍|國籍，]]然而印度政府至2010年代尚未就該事件給予受害印度華人一個正式的道歉，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Chinese Indians in Canada commemorate 50th anniversary of internment at Deoli Camp|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2012/11/16/chinese_indians_in_canada_commemorate_50th_anniversary_of_internment_at_deoli_camp.html|accessdate=2021-01-20|date=2012-11-16|work=thestar.com|language=en|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202124244/http://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2012/11/16/chinese_indians_in_canada_commemorate_50th_anniversary_of_internment_at_deoli_camp.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>或向受到影響的華裔印度公民作出賠償。<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=In Canada, Indian mission refuses to acknowledge a Chinese-Indian protest – and a historic wrong|url=https://scroll.in/article/848781/in-canada-indian-mission-refuses-to-acknowledge-a-chinese-indian-protest-and-a-historic-wrong|accessdate=2021-01-20|last=D’Souza|first=Dilip|work=Scroll.in|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207231946/https://scroll.in/article/848781/in-canada-indian-mission-refuses-to-acknowledge-a-chinese-indian-protest-and-a-historic-wrong|dead-url=no}}</ref>

